The paper deals with image processing and specifically focuses on edge detection in facial and remotely sensed images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of statistical methods, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper deals with image analysis, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
